Privacy Policy
At Counter, we take the privacy of our users very seriously. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use and protect the personal information that you provide when using our application.
Information gathering:
Counter does not collect any personal data. We do not request or store any personally identifiable information such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, etc.
Use of information:
The sole purpose of Counter is to provide our users with an easy way to make lists and count time. We do not use your personal information for any other purpose.
